<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0a173b;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 150px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <!-- Header -->
    <div
      class="header"
      style="
        background-color: #0a173b;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
      "
    >
      <img
        src="https://va-claims-assets.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/VA_Claims_Main_Logo_Transparent_2_200px.png"
        alt="VA Claims Academy Logo"
        style="max-width: 100px; height: auto"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Email Body -->
    <div style="padding: 20px">
      <p style="font-size: 16px">Hi <%= name %>,</p>

      <p>
        We hope this email finds you well. We're reaching out to remind you
        about completing the supplemental form for your VA claim.
      </p>

      <p>
        This form is essential for providing additional information to support
        your claim. Please take a moment to complete it as soon as possible.
      </p>

      <p><%= message %></p>

      <p>
        You can access the supplemental form <a href="<%= formLink %>">here</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you need any assistance or have questions about the form, our team is
        here to help.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        We hope this email finds you well! We're reaching out about an important
        next step in strengthening your VA claim.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        It's time to dive into your Detail Builders! These are crucial pieces in
        building a more powerful case for your benefits.
        <strong style="color: #0a173b"
          >Now's the perfect time to complete them and add more weight to your
          claim!</strong
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        <strong style="color: #0a173b"
          >Every detail you provide brings you closer to securing the benefits
          you've earned. This is your chance to make your case even
          stronger.</strong
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        Ready to take this important step? Just click the button below to access
        and complete your Detail Builders:
      </p>

      <p style="text-align: center">
        <a
          href="<%= formLink %>"
          style="
            background-color: #0a173b;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
          "
          >Complete Your Detail Builders</a
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        Keep pushing forward â€“ you're making great progress!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div
      style="
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        padding-top: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      "
    >
      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        In your corner,<br />
        VA Claims Academy Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
